@CasbinMinimalApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:8680

### Liste des voisins
GET {{CasbinMinimalApi_HostAddress}}/api/neighbors
Accept: application/json

### Création d'un voisin
POST {{CasbinMinimalApi_HostAddress}}/api/neighbors
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "Alice Martin",
  "email": "alice.martin@example.com",
  "address": {
    "street": "12 rue des Lilas",
    "city": "Lyon",
    "zipCode": "69000"
  }
}

### Récupération d'un voisin par id (utilise l'id capturé)
GET {{CasbinMinimalApi_HostAddress}}/api/neighbors/1
Accept: application/json

### Mise à jour d'un voisin
PUT {{CasbinMinimalApi_HostAddress}}/api/neighbors/1
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "Alice M. (updated)",
  "email": "alice.updated@example.com",
  "address": {
    "street": "99 avenue Centrale",
    "city": "Lyon",
    "zipCode": "69001"
  }
}

### Suppression d'un voisin
DELETE {{CasbinMinimalApi_HostAddress}}/api/neighbors/1
Accept: application/json